node.title: Australian cricketer Tim Paine stands down as Test captain
node.alt: Wearing a green blazer, whites and a pink baggy cap, Tim Paine walks through up the SCG race past members seats
node.description: Australian cricketer Tim Paine has stood down as Test captain over a sexting incident from four years ago. Follow live.
node.content: ["Australian Test cricket captain Tim Paine has called a press conference to make an announcement.", "Follow live."]
